message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper discusses the use of deep learning-based methods for medical image segmentation, specifically for multi-organ segmentation of 3D CT images. This topic falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), medical imaging (cs.MED), and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
